Body:
Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Thanks for applying to the {{RoleName}} position at {{ShopName}}. We received your application and will be in touch shortly with next steps.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Please complete this short pre-screen so we can move your application forward:
{{PrescreenFormLink}}

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

We would like to schedule a phone screen for the {{RoleName}} role. Please pick a time here:
{{BookingLink}}

Looking forward to talking.

{{HiringManagerName}}
{{ShopName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Your phone screen is confirmed for {{InterviewDate}}.
Meeting link: {{MeetLink}}

Talk soon,
{{HiringManagerName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Great conversation. The next step is a full interview at {{InterviewLocation}}. Please choose a time:
{{FullInterviewLink}}

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

We are moving forward with your application for {{RoleName}}. Please share up to 3 references using this form:
{{CandRefFormLink}}

Thanks,
{{HiringManagerName}}

Hi {{ReferenceName}},

{{CandidateName}} is being considered for our {{RoleName}} position and listed you as a reference. Please complete this short form:
{{RefCheckFormLink}}

Thank you,
{{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Please complete this short assessment so we can finalize your fit for {{RoleName}}:
{{CultureFormLink}}

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Your live interview went well and you are now in the final stage. Please complete BOTH of the following by {{ResponseDeadline}} (within the next 48–72 hours):

1) References — share up to 3:
   {{CandRefFormLink}}

2) Culture Fit assessment:
   {{CultureFormLink}}

Completing both keeps your application moving without delay.

Thanks,
{{HiringManagerName}}
{{ShopName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

We would like to invite you to a paid working interview at {{InterviewLocation}}. Reply with a couple of days and times that work for you over the next week and we will lock it in.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

We appreciate your interest in {{ShopName}}. We are still reviewing applicants and will follow up within {{SLADays}} business days.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Thank you for applying for the {{RoleName}} role at {{ShopName}}. After review, we will not be moving forward at this time. We wish you the best.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

We are reviewing your application. You will hear from us within {{SLADays}} business days. In the meantime, learn more at {{ShopWebsite}}.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

We are finalizing the offer for {{RoleName}}. {{HiringManagerName}} will reach out shortly with the details.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Congratulations — we are excited to welcome you as our new {{RoleName}}. {{HiringManagerName}} will follow up with start details for {{InterviewLocation}}.

— {{CompanySignatureName}}

Hi {{CandidateFirstName}},

Thanks for completing the pre-screen for the {{RoleName}} position at {{ShopName}}. To move forward, please complete both of the following BEFORE your phone screen:

1) Book your phone screen with {{HiringManagerName}}:
   {{BookingLink}}

2) Complete the Technician Skill Level Test (takes ~20 minutes):
   {{SkillsTestLink}}

The skill test helps us understand your hands-on experience so we can use the phone screen to talk about the work, not the basics. Please complete the test on your own without outside assistance — we look for honest, real-world answers.

Looking forward to talking.

{{HiringManagerName}}
{{ShopName}}
